long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f:
Beautify your new tab page with a useful, beautiful and fun theme.
Game Wallpaper New Tab is here to enhance your new tab experience.
Choose the background theme of your favorite game, make your daily trip quickly thanks to the social media icons.

All in one tab.

Click 'ADD TO CHROME' to install the Game Wallpaper New Tab extension.

Main Features:
* Choose from among many game background images and change them
* Select preferred background change feature from settings menu
* Quickly access your social media accounts
* Popular games menu for fun
* Follow the time, date and day information from the top right
* Search the internet quickly and accurately using the search box in the middle top

Note: For the best experience, click the "Keep changes" button after installing Game Wallpaper New Tab. This will show Game Wallpaper Theme on every new tab as intended.

➤ Background:
Game Wallpaper New Tab offers a selection of backgrounds with many games directly in the new tab. Change background images with few clicks from new tab.

➤ The Game Wallpaper New Tab theme contains the background image of the following games:

The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom
Minecraft
League of Legends
Injustice
GTA 5 (Grand Theft Auto 5)
The Witcher 3 Wild Hunt
PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS
Fortnite: Battle Royale
fallout
The Legend Of Zelda Breath Of The Wild
Red Dead Redemption 2
Call of Duty Warzone
Call Of Duty Modern Warfare


For more information about privacy and Eula, visit:
https://wallpapertab.com/privacy-policy/
